==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subcaliber
<hw>Sub*cal"i*ber</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Smaller than the
caliber of a firearm.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>subcalibre</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Subcaliber projectile</b></col>, <cd>a projectile having
a smaller diameter than the caliber of the arm from which it is fired,
and to which it is fitted by means of a sabot.</cd>
<au>Knight.</au></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subcarbonate</ent>⟦br⟧
